{"type": "article", "id": 16363, "title": "汉堡灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-21T06:58:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607172148RWnQFaDp62hbcYEd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款充满童趣的汉堡灯是万圣节必备，白天它只是引人发笑的装饰，但在黑暗中点亮时就能看到透着白光的眼睛和獠牙，完全是一个南瓜头。既可以捉弄小朋友，也不会显得太过惊悚。灯高 30 厘米，在 2002 就已经出售了，<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/cn/undercover-hamburger-lamp\" target=\"_blank\">最近改进细节重新出售。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143650GbCoUJ08BLKPId9X.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143651MUgpEzwuJn3tYkFT.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143651YJ3rBRKzMnVmUiFd.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143652DE8tYzZ7AHNa4OKd.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}